## Quality Checklist

When implementing or reviewing (focus: general):

- [ ] Discovered project structure and matched existing patterns
- [ ] Correct layer: HTTP hook vs preload bridge vs local UI state
- [ ] Reused existing component / form control / API module where possible
- [ ] Query keys and cache invalidation consistent with the project
- [ ] Form validation schema and accessible error display
- [ ] Theme tokens / design system — no stray magic values
- [ ] IPC fully wired (handler, allowlist, preload, types) with path validation
- [ ] No `electron` imports in renderer; `contextIsolation` respected
- [ ] `npm run lint` passes
- [ ] `npm run build` passes
- [ ] Project test script passes (when defined in `package.json`)

Provide concrete suggestions with file paths and short examples grounded in **this** repository.
